parameters.DryLevel: 0: The level of the dry signal (dB). The value is between -20 and 10.

parameters.WetLevel: 1: The level of the early reflection signal (wet signal) (dB). The value is between -20 and 10.

parameters.RoomSize: 2: The room size of the reflection. The value is between 0 and 100.

parameters.WetDelay: 3: The length of the initial delay of the wet signal (ms). The value is between 0 and 200.

parameters.Strength: 4: The reverberation strength. The value is between 0 and 100.
